title: STEREO Behind IMPACT State of Health  - J. Luhmann (UCB/SSL)

info.x_cadence_note: Counts based on variable 'Epoch' in https://cdaweb.gsfc.nasa.gov/sp_phys/data/stereo/behind/l1/impact/hkp/2006/stb_l1_impact_hkp_20061028_v02.cdf. The most common cadence occurred for 98.7189% of the 8862 timesteps. Cadence = 2000 [ms] = PT2S.
